Localization.Name: Quartz "Black Op" Energy SMG
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Verified Offworld Laser Technologies
Item Type: SMG
Class: Energy (Electron)

Battery Size: 50
Rate of Fire: Beam
Effective Range: 15-20 m

Attachments: Optics (S1), Underbarrel (S1)

Manufacturer VOLT's Quartz SMG utilizes exciting new weapon technology that fires a short range beam that fractures into multiple beams the longer it fires, making it an extremely effective close quarter weapon.

The green glow of the Quartz's barrel pops against the all black look of the "Black Op" edition.

Localization.Name: NV-TAC
Localization.Description: High-end company known for manufacturing technically precise and experimental optics and weapon attachments. Founded in 2811, NV-TAC initially built sensors for long-range scanning stations and surveying operations before shifting operations to the more profitable personal weapon market. Seen by some as too expensive and feature-dense, but beloved by soldiers and security professionals for their durable design, precision adjustments, and reliable performance.

Localization.Name: Gamma "Black Op" (1x Holographic)
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: NV-TAC
Type: Projection 
Attachment Point: Optic
Magnification: 1x
Aim Time: +15%
Size: 1

Whether under the blazing sun or on the dark side of a moon, the NV-TAC Gamma projects an easy to see reticle to help ensure your shot finds its mark.

The "Black Op" scope variant is black.
